<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Edsan Transient House and Inland Resort Management System</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #6e1c94;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header img {
            max-width: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .header h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
        }

        /* Search Bar styles */
        .search-bar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0px 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            max-width: 1000px;
            width: 80%;
            margin: 30px auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .search-bar div {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 0 15px;
            border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .search-bar div:last-child {
            border-right: none;
        }

        .search-bar label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .search-bar select,
        .search-bar input {
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #333;
            padding: 5px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .search-bar select::placeholder,
        .search-bar input::placeholder {
            color: #aaa;
        }

        .search-bar button {
            background-color: #FF5A5F;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .search-bar button i {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
        }

        ul {
            padding-left: 0; /* Remove default padding */
            list-style-type: none; /* Remove default bullets */
        }

        li::before {
            content: "\2022"; /* Unicode for bullet point */
            color: #333; /* Bullet color */
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block; 
            width: 1em; /* Adjust width to control distance between bullet and text */
            margin-left: -1em; /* Adjust margin to move bullet closer to text */
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Adjust space between list items */
        }

        .branches {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .contact {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .contact h3 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .contact p {
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* Responsive Styles */
        @@media (max-width: 768px) {
            .search-bar {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: stretch;
                padding: 20px;
                width: 90%;
            }

            .search-bar div {
                padding: 10px 0;
                border-right: none;
            }

            .search-bar select,
            .search-bar input {
                width: 100%;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .search-bar button {
                width: 100%;
                margin-top: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <div class="header">
        <h1>EDSAN</h1>
        <h2>TRANSIENT HOUSE AND RESORT MANAGEMENT SYSTEM</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Search Bar -->
    <form asp-action="Search" asp-controller="Room" method="post">
        <div class="search-bar">
            <div>
                <label for="location">Where</label>
                <select id="location" name="location">
                    <option value="Champaca">Champaca</option>
                    <option value="Mati">Mati</option>
                    <option value="Pantukan">Pantukan</option>
                    <option value="Tacunan">Tacunan</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            @{
                var today = DateTime.Now;
                var tomorrow = today.AddDays(1);
            }

            <div>
                <label for="checkin">Check in</label>
                <input type="date" id="checkin" name="checkInDate" value="@today.ToString("yyyy-MM-dd")" placeholder="Add dates">
            </div>
            <div>
                <label for="checkout">Check out</label>
                <input type="date" id="checkout" name="checkOutDate" value="@tomorrow.ToString("yyyy-MM-dd")" placeholder="Add dates">
            </div>
            <div>
                <label for="guests">Number of Guests</label>
                <input type="number" id="guests" name="guests" value="2" min="1" max="20" class="form-control" style="height: 30px; font-size: 14px;">
            </div>

            <button type="submit">
                <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
            </button>
        </div>
    </form>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <div class="content">
        <p>
            Edsan Transient House and Inland Resort Management System is a comprehensive platform designed to streamline operations.
        </p>
        <p>
            It offers an intuitive interface for:
            <ul>
                <li>Managing room bookings.</li>
                <li>Handling guest check-ins.</li>
                <li>Processing payments.</li>
                <li>Managing resort amenities.</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <p>
            The system is tailored to meet the unique needs of both small and large hospitality businesses.
        </p>
        <p>
            Ensures efficient management and an enhanced guest experience.
        </p>
        <p>
            Provides tools to manage your property with ease and professionalism, whether handling daily operations or optimizing service offerings.
        </p>

        <div class="branches">
            <strong>Branches:</strong> Champaca • Mati • Pantukan • Tacunan
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <div class="contact">
        <h3>Contact below:</h3>
        <p>Eduardo Santander/09326068646</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
